nodes.text: This city was a major city on Concordia during the Clone Wars. Governor Pre Vizsla maintained a residence at the government complex there. In 21 BBY Obi-Wan Kenobi and Duchess Satine Kryze visited with the body of the Death Watch bomber who destroyed the Peace Park.
This unnamed city first appeared in Star Wars canon in the twelfth episode of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series' second season, entitled "The Mandalore Plot".
